Class PropertiesManager

java.lang.Object
com.amiasya.core.manager.PropertiesManager
public class PropertiesManager extends Object
PropertiesManager is the class that manages your Locale Interface (ChatProvider) To be honest most of the methods here are useless for you. However, there are two utilties method that you can use
